n class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">for</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">&quot;name&quot;</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">标签</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/label&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;input</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">type</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">&quot;text&quot;</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">class</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">&quot;form-control&quot;</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">placeholder</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">&quot;文本输入&quot;</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\"> &nbsp;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/div&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/form&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\"></span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/body&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\"></span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/html&gt;</span></pre><p><a href=\"/try/try2.php?filename=bootstrap3-form-inputs\" target=\"_blank\"><button class=\"btn example-btn\">尝试一下 »</button></a></p><p>结果如下所示：</p><div class=\"cover\" style=\"border: 1px solid #D6D6D6;padding: 5px;\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/inputs_demo.jpg\" alt=\"输入框\"/></div><h3>文本框（Textarea）</h3><p>当您需要进行多行输入的时，则可以使用文本框 textarea。必要时可以改变 <em>rows</em> 属性（较少的行 = 较小的盒子，较多的行 = 较大的盒子）。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit prettyprinted\"><span class=\"dec\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\"></span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;html&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\"></span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;head&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\"> &nbsp; </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">Bootstrap 实例 - 文本框</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\"> &nbsp; </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;link</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">rel</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">&quot;